data.description: Welcome to 2008 Riverview! From updates to style, location and more, this home offers so much. The living room offers a stone gas fireplace, vaulted ceiling with wooden beams and wall of windows for lots of natural light.  L shaped kitchen with glass backsplash and plenty of windows to enjoy the view.  Master bedroom with built in cabinets and full bath. Newly remodeled guest bathroom rounds out the main floor. Game room with gas fireplace open to additional room which allows for plenty of room for entertaining. Covered side porch overlooks newly installed salt water pool with heater. Nice deck to relax by the pool as well as stamped concrete pad.
